WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: -RrcSukxuSM

NOTE Language: en

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:08.890
It is a great pleasure for Me,

00:00:10.890 --> 00:00:12.940
greatest joy

00:00:13.880 --> 00:00:17.000
to see so many Sahaja Yogis

00:00:19.531 --> 00:00:21.940
for the Guru Puja.

00:00:23.890 --> 00:00:25.960
It’s very gratifying

00:00:27.404 --> 00:00:30.930
to think that there are so many,

00:00:31.539 --> 00:00:39.820
so many of you who are disciples.

00:00:47.980 --> 00:00:50.890
It was never expected

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:54.820
that I’ll have so many,

00:00:55.460 --> 00:01:00.980
so many people following Me.

00:01:05.900 --> 00:01:15.980
It is being expected

00:01:18.840 --> 00:01:20.820
that you all will

00:01:22.860 --> 00:01:29.790
follow My message of Love.

00:01:33.010 --> 00:01:38.980
I do not have to say anything for Love.

00:01:41.860 --> 00:01:50.930
Love is absolute gift,

00:01:54.810 --> 00:02:01.790
gift of just feeling others.

00:02:04.790 --> 00:02:08.980
There is no talking about it,

00:02:09.860 --> 00:02:13.780
discussing about it, nothing;

00:02:14.780 --> 00:02:20.930
just you feel that Love.

00:02:24.930 --> 00:02:32.890
To feel the Love, I would say, one has to have a heart,

00:02:33.870 --> 00:02:36.780
but how can you have a heart?

00:02:37.930 --> 00:02:44.810
It is not your own doing, it’s all there.

00:02:47.010 --> 00:02:55.950
So, it is something is already gifted to you, you have it,

00:02:57.790 --> 00:02:59.970
that you can feel that Love.

00:03:02.980 --> 00:03:09.010
It’s so much joy - giving, peace - giving.

00:03:10.790 --> 00:03:17.780
Love has its own qualities

00:03:19.000 --> 00:03:25.830
and one of the qualities is that Love understands.

00:03:26.900 --> 00:03:29.900
Its understanding is not in words,

00:03:30.840 --> 00:03:32.780
not in thought,

00:03:33.860 --> 00:03:36.780
but understands within.

00:03:39.830 --> 00:03:41.950
It can feel within,

00:03:45.780 --> 00:03:47.010
which is very important.

00:03:50.780 --> 00:03:52.950
This is the most important part

00:03:54.820 --> 00:03:56.890
one has to realize

00:03:58.920 --> 00:04:04.840
that Love you can only feel it.

00:04:05.920 --> 00:04:08.790
You cannot talk about it,

00:04:09.840 --> 00:04:11.920
you cannot show about it,

00:04:12.920 --> 00:04:16.010
but it is within and you can feel it.

00:04:19.890 --> 00:04:21.930
And that is why today

00:04:22.810 --> 00:04:30.890
is your celebration of the Guru.

00:04:33.970 --> 00:04:36.000
It’s the celebration where

00:04:38.970 --> 00:04:45.810
you can feel that Love for your Guru.

00:04:46.970 --> 00:04:51.950
That feeling is within

00:04:53.870 --> 00:04:58.860
and only in within you can feel that.

00:04:59.970 --> 00:05:05.940
So, we have to understand it’s not the show,

00:05:07.840 --> 00:05:12.010
it’s nothing else but just the feeling within

00:05:13.000 --> 00:05:19.970
that you know that you have Love of the Divine.

00:05:22.920 --> 00:05:24.930
This you can have because

00:05:26.790 --> 00:05:30.010
it is just there.

00:05:30.980 --> 00:05:32.970
No one can give you,

00:05:34.010 --> 00:05:36.790
no one can sell it,

00:05:37.780 --> 00:05:41.870
no one can share it - it’s just there.

00:05:43.810 --> 00:05:49.810
And that Love has to be felt and shared.

00:05:51.810 --> 00:05:56.000
It has nothing to do with others;

00:05:57.950 --> 00:06:01.980
whether others love you or not makes no difference.

00:06:03.920 --> 00:06:06.810
It’s within yourself,

00:06:07.920 --> 00:06:09.790
this feeling,

00:06:10.810 --> 00:06:15.970
this depth is there which you enjoy.

00:06:22.910 --> 00:06:26.910
It is the capacity -

00:06:27.990 --> 00:06:32.860
every one has this, lots of it.

00:06:34.830 --> 00:06:39.000
Sometimes you feel it, you have lost it;

00:06:39.800 --> 00:06:42.890
Sometimes you feel you have gained it.

00:06:43.830 --> 00:06:54.850
But it is there as much as the expanse of a sea.

00:06:55.830 --> 00:06:57.930
Sea, you cannot say

00:06:58.850 --> 00:07:01.990
today is full and tomorrow is not.

00:07:02.910 --> 00:07:04.910
It is eternal.

00:07:05.930 --> 00:07:12.860
In the same way, the source of your Love is eternal.

00:07:14.800 --> 00:07:21.960
You cannot measure it,

00:07:27.930 --> 00:07:30.830
it’s difficult.

00:07:33.020 --> 00:07:37.890
But it’s beyond all your human expressions

00:07:38.890 --> 00:07:49.910
and it shows your understanding,

00:07:51.830 --> 00:07:53.930
your understanding of Love,

00:07:54.860 --> 00:07:56.910
which has no words,

00:07:57.940 --> 00:07:59.930
which cannot explain;

00:08:00.940 --> 00:08:03.880
but by itself you will know

00:08:04.850 --> 00:08:08.910
that "I have this quality to love

00:08:09.830 --> 00:08:11.930
within myself

00:08:12.850 --> 00:08:17.940
and I can enjoy with this Love within myself."

00:08:18.930 --> 00:08:28.860
This is a very unique gift

00:08:30.020 --> 00:08:38.830
which only very few human beings have.

00:08:41.860 --> 00:08:46.940
Among animals also you find people who have love,

00:08:47.990 --> 00:08:52.830
but that love is not deep,

00:08:53.800 --> 00:08:56.800
that love has no meaning.

00:08:59.910 --> 00:09:03.880
It has some purpose maybe,

00:09:04.830 --> 00:09:07.010
but it is not human,

00:09:08.820 --> 00:09:12.960
so, it lacks the beauty of human Love,

00:09:13.960 --> 00:09:21.910
It lacks the understanding of human Love.

00:09:25.960 --> 00:09:28.020
It is not easy to describe

00:09:28.970 --> 00:09:34.020
or explain Love in human words.

00:09:35.880 --> 00:09:39.830
This you can only feel within your Self.

00:09:41.790 --> 00:09:44.930
That is what, once you start feeling,

00:09:45.800 --> 00:09:50.930
you can feel who is your Guru,

00:09:52.880 --> 00:10:00.970
Whom do you think you are being taught

00:10:01.020 --> 00:10:08.830
and persuaded and made to live in a particular manner.

00:10:09.850 --> 00:10:11.930
All that is possible.

00:10:15.790 --> 00:10:17.020
Everything is possible,

00:10:17.860 --> 00:10:19.830
humanly possible,

00:10:19.940 --> 00:10:25.820
but to love and to enjoy Love

00:10:25.870 --> 00:10:28.850
is not so easy,

00:10:29.800 --> 00:10:33.900
unless and until you are immersed in it.

00:10:39.960 --> 00:10:42.790
It’s very gratifying,

00:10:42.970 --> 00:10:47.970
it is very lovable

00:10:49.820 --> 00:10:52.960
to see how people love each other

00:10:55.960 --> 00:11:04.020
and then this Love spreads.

00:11:06.930 --> 00:11:09.970
Love begets Love.

00:11:11.930 --> 00:11:19.790
If somebody has Love, it just spreads.

00:11:20.800 --> 00:11:22.830
You need not tell anyone,

00:11:23.940 --> 00:11:25.990
you need not confess it,

00:11:26.800 --> 00:11:30.880
but it will spread.

00:11:31.910 --> 00:11:36.940
And this is what one has to learn,

00:11:38.890 --> 00:11:43.940
how to see that Love in other person.

00:11:48.910 --> 00:11:50.850
Somehow,

00:11:51.910 --> 00:11:56.920
we are here already in Love

00:11:57.910 --> 00:12:02.020
because of Sahaj happening.

00:12:03.000 --> 00:12:05.970
We all love

00:12:06.890 --> 00:12:08.920
and we enjoy love,

00:12:09.860 --> 00:12:11.880
shows on our faces

00:12:12.860 --> 00:12:15.020
that we are in Love;

00:12:15.990 --> 00:12:18.800
in our characters,

00:12:20.830 --> 00:12:22.810
in our lives,

00:12:23.000 --> 00:12:25.800
that we are in Love.

00:12:26.890 --> 00:12:28.830
What a thing,

00:12:28.980 --> 00:12:32.910
which is not very normal,

00:12:32.970 --> 00:12:35.020
becomes so normal

00:12:35.940 --> 00:12:38.860
and so easily available.

00:12:39.830 --> 00:12:42.920
It is a very big blessing

00:12:43.920 --> 00:12:46.020
that you are human beings

00:12:46.910 --> 00:12:52.870
and that this source of Love

00:12:53.910 --> 00:12:59.860
is there, plus the feeling for Love is there.

00:13:00.830 --> 00:13:05.020
It’s a very intricate situation

00:13:05.920 --> 00:13:09.830
which cannot be explained in words,

00:13:11.870 --> 00:13:15.840
only one can be in it

00:13:15.920 --> 00:13:17.950
and enjoy it.

00:13:20.860 --> 00:13:22.910
So today is the day

00:13:22.970 --> 00:13:29.000
when we are celebrating the Guru Puja.

00:13:31.860 --> 00:13:38.920
The greatest Guru that we have is Love,

00:13:39.890 --> 00:13:46.840
Sahaj Love. It's the Guru within us which teaches us,

00:13:47.780 --> 00:13:49.940
which somehow or other leads us.

00:13:50.940 --> 00:13:55.020
We are lead into that

00:13:55.920 --> 00:14:02.880
great line of understanding,

00:14:03.970 --> 00:14:07.860
for which we don’t have to go to any college,

00:14:07.970 --> 00:14:10.940
to any school for education.

00:14:11.840 --> 00:14:14.780
It is something so much within

00:14:14.950 --> 00:14:24.910
that it works and expresses itself,

00:14:25.800 --> 00:14:28.940
expresses like a light.

00:14:29.880 --> 00:14:33.830
Such people we can make out because

00:14:33.980 --> 00:14:36.860
they are fully enlightened.

00:14:37.840 --> 00:14:39.830
They have light

00:14:39.980 --> 00:14:42.800
and through that light they see

00:14:42.940 --> 00:14:44.870
the whole world,

00:14:45.000 --> 00:14:49.780
which is very innocent and simple for them.

00:14:57.810 --> 00:15:03.890
We have love for our children naturally,

00:15:04.810 --> 00:15:07.880
we have love for our parents naturally.

00:15:08.840 --> 00:15:12.780
We have love for some people;

00:15:12.910 --> 00:15:14.940
but that love is different

00:15:15.780 --> 00:15:18.860
from God’s Love, I’m telling you.

00:15:20.000 --> 00:15:23.910
That has some connections,

00:15:24.780 --> 00:15:25.990
some meanings

00:15:26.830 --> 00:15:35.970
but this Love which is -

00:15:38.880 --> 00:15:43.910
cannot be described in words,

00:15:44.000 --> 00:15:46.890
has to be felt within.

00:15:49.860 --> 00:15:52.980
Same, when you talk of your Guru,

00:15:54.830 --> 00:15:59.020
you should have that Love within you.

00:16:01.780 --> 00:16:05.860
Why do you feel it so much?

00:16:08.970 --> 00:16:14.910
The reason is, Guru loves you

00:16:15.920 --> 00:16:17.970
and you love Guru;

00:16:18.910 --> 00:16:21.020
That’s the only reason

00:16:21.920 --> 00:16:24.890
why should you love your Guru.

00:16:25.840 --> 00:16:28.020
Now, there's no reason for that.

00:16:28.950 --> 00:16:31.830
Because Love is Love.

00:16:32.860 --> 00:16:34.840
and that is how

00:16:35.860 --> 00:16:40.020
the Guru becomes very important in life.

00:16:41.800 --> 00:16:43.800
We have people

00:16:44.000 --> 00:16:47.950
who love their Guru

00:16:49.860 --> 00:16:51.940
and are very much

00:16:53.970 --> 00:17:02.800
in chaste understanding of their Love.

00:17:04.910 --> 00:17:09.830
In this great opportunity of Love that we are,

00:17:10.840 --> 00:17:16.940
we are here to enjoy each other fully,

00:17:17.910 --> 00:17:19.860
from our heart,

00:17:20.880 --> 00:17:26.940
that there is this ocean within us,

00:17:28.830 --> 00:17:32.810
we have to just get submerged in that ocean.

00:17:32.940 --> 00:17:35.800
If we are lost in that ocean,

00:17:35.920 --> 00:17:39.940
then we’ll have no problems,

00:17:41.810 --> 00:17:43.860
no questions.

00:17:44.890 --> 00:17:47.910
Everything will be our own

00:17:48.890 --> 00:17:50.880
and we can manage

00:17:50.990 --> 00:17:55.880
everything without any argument,

00:17:55.950 --> 00:17:59.000
without any questioning.

00:18:01.000 --> 00:18:05.020
That is what is being Sahaj.

00:18:05.850 --> 00:18:08.810
The Sahaj way, if you have

00:18:08.940 --> 00:18:12.830
this Love, you enjoy.

00:18:12.950 --> 00:18:16.810
You enjoy yourself and enjoy everybody else,

00:18:16.880 --> 00:18:18.990
because it is Sahaj.

00:18:19.830 --> 00:18:21.910
Don’t have to make any efforts,

00:18:22.780 --> 00:18:24.880
don’t have to try anything.

00:18:24.970 --> 00:18:27.990
Just it is there and it works.

00:18:33.860 --> 00:18:40.880
The feeling of Love

00:18:41.990 --> 00:18:47.890
has no way of expressing itself.

00:18:49.020 --> 00:18:51.860
It is just there,

00:18:52.810 --> 00:18:54.850
it cannot express,

00:18:55.990 --> 00:19:00.970
because it is without expression.

00:19:02.840 --> 00:19:08.000
It is just to be felt within yourself.

00:19:09.880 --> 00:19:12.990
Then you want to do so many things:

00:19:14.000 --> 00:19:16.830
you want to help everyone,

00:19:16.990 --> 00:19:19.830
you want to help yourself,

00:19:20.810 --> 00:19:24.940
you want to do good to others.

00:19:25.860 --> 00:19:30.970
So much has been done by great leaders of the world

00:19:31.830 --> 00:19:33.990
because they had that Love.

00:19:34.850 --> 00:19:37.780
They had nothing else but this Love

00:19:37.970 --> 00:19:41.920
which they could not contain them within themselves,

00:19:41.990 --> 00:19:46.020
so, they tried to spread it.

00:19:46.920 --> 00:19:50.940
And they are called now as our Guru,

00:19:51.860 --> 00:19:53.940
as our masters.

00:19:54.840 --> 00:19:56.980
With that Love within,

00:19:57.980 --> 00:20:04.020
which approached people in that unique manner.

00:20:05.850 --> 00:20:07.990
That’s the thing that

00:20:09.910 --> 00:20:11.980
we cannot possess,

00:20:12.830 --> 00:20:14.870
you cannot claim -

00:20:16.020 --> 00:20:18.020
it is there

00:20:18.980 --> 00:20:21.020
and it works,

00:20:22.840 --> 00:20:24.870
it works automatically.

00:20:26.960 --> 00:20:28.980
This is what we have to know,

00:20:29.790 --> 00:20:35.900
that we are that Love.

00:20:37.860 --> 00:20:38.980
That Love is within us.

00:20:39.800 --> 00:20:43.980
We have to have knowledge,

00:20:44.920 --> 00:20:48.840
we have to have a complete knowledge

00:20:48.970 --> 00:20:53.800
that we are that Love.

00:20:54.950 --> 00:20:57.940
That will solve our problem,

00:20:58.990 --> 00:21:00.950
because you can explain everything,

00:21:01.020 --> 00:21:02.950
all your behaviour,

00:21:03.890 --> 00:21:05.780
all your failures,

00:21:05.840 --> 00:21:07.990
everything you can explain

00:21:08.800 --> 00:21:13.810
when you know that you are endowed with that Love.

00:21:16.780 --> 00:21:18.950
This is what is the Guru

00:21:19.860 --> 00:21:22.810
is the Love within you

00:21:23.780 --> 00:21:25.020
which wants to share

00:21:25.890 --> 00:21:27.920
Love with others,

00:21:29.800 --> 00:21:32.990
which wants to give Love to others.

00:21:37.780 --> 00:21:42.840
This is what is peace and joy.

00:21:43.980 --> 00:21:46.950
I can go on talking on Love,

00:21:48.000 --> 00:21:51.950
but to feel it

00:21:54.790 --> 00:21:57.930
within yourself is the biggest thing.

00:21:58.980 --> 00:22:00.870
Like water:

00:22:01.010 --> 00:22:02.960
if you are thirsty,

00:22:03.870 --> 00:22:05.840
we can give you water,

00:22:06.020 --> 00:22:07.980
but we cannot drink.

00:22:08.850 --> 00:22:10.850
You have to drink water

00:22:10.950 --> 00:22:13.010
and you have to

00:22:15.910 --> 00:22:17.950
feel the taste,

00:22:18.870 --> 00:22:20.810
feel the feeling,

00:22:20.930 --> 00:22:22.880
what it does,

00:22:22.980 --> 00:22:27.020
and all that is together,

00:22:28.020 --> 00:22:30.880
that’s not separate.

00:22:31.850 --> 00:22:32.990
I don’t think the subject

00:22:33.790 --> 00:22:35.960
was too subtle for you people.

00:22:36.880 --> 00:22:39.880
You all have reached a certain amount

00:22:40.020 --> 00:22:42.990
of understanding of that Love.

00:22:44.950 --> 00:22:48.850
I hope, it grows

00:22:49.810 --> 00:22:51.900
and you grow into it,

00:22:52.010 --> 00:22:55.870
all of you, and enjoy it.

00:22:56.020 --> 00:22:58.920
May God bless you!
